        "cooked": "<p>Released to production a long time ago:</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/6325622209178-Text-Formatting\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      \n\n      <a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/6325622209178-Text-Formatting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Signal Support</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/6325622209178-Text-Formatting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Text Formatting</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Highlight your selected text to use bold, italics, strikethrough, monospace, or a *spoiler* that taps to reveal.\n\nCompose a message.\nBefore hitting send, highlight the text you want to format. A me...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
